                                                                                                                                Input and selection

                                                                                                                                Slider

                                                                                                                                Stable

                                                                                                                                A slider allows users to select a single numeric value or a range between minimum and maximum values.

                                                                                                                                Usage
                                                                                                                                Specs
                                                                                                                                Status & changelog
                                                                                                                                Common Alternative names
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Range, range input, range slider


                                                                                                                                Questions, comments, feedback?

                                                                                                                                Leave a comment in Figma or reach out to us on Slack.

                                                                                                                                #base-design-support

                                                                                                                                  

                                                                                                                                Anatomy

                                                                                                                                A slider is, at minimum, made of a track and knob(s).

                                                                                                                                The slider can have one knob for the user to select a single value or two knobs to select a range.

                                                                                                                                Simple
                                                                                                                                Icons
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Optional icons can be placed on the ends of the track to illustrate maximum and minimum values.

                                                                                                                                Label
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Knobs can include Label values for a more precise selection for the user.

                                                                                                                                Range
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                The slider can two knobs for the user to select a range.

                                                                                                                                Segment
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                The track can have ticks for a more precise and accurate experience.

                                                                                                                                Usage

                                                                                                                                Use sliders to allow users to select a value or range from all the options available. Icons or labels can be placed on the ends of the track to represent a numeric or relative range.

                                                                                                                                Use sliders when users could benefit from receiving immediate feedback.


                                                                                                                                Types of sliders

                                                                                                                                Continuous

                                                                                                                                Users select a value from a continuous horizontal track.

                                                                                                                                Discrete

                                                                                                                                Users select a value from a segmented horizontal track with predefined values. Discrete sliders makes it easier for the user to select a specific value in the range.

                                                                                                                                Do
                                                                                                                                Do use a continous slider to allow users to select from a subjective range
                                                                                                                                Don’t
                                                                                                                                Don’t use a discrete slider to allow users to select from a subjective range

                                                                                                                                Provide context

                                                                                                                                Do
                                                                                                                                Do provide context with labels and/or icons
                                                                                                                                Don’t
                                                                                                                                Don’t exclude labels and/or icons because users may be uncertain of the purpose of the slider.
                                                                                                                                Do
                                                                                                                                Do write short and concise instructional labels in sentence case for easy readability
                                                                                                                                Don’t
                                                                                                                                Don’t write long labels in title case, since it is more difficult for the user to read


                                                                                                                                Immediate feedback

                                                                                                                                Sliders should demonstrate the full range of options that are available to the user and provide immediate feedback to allow users to make their decision. Consider providing live feedback for the user as the value changes.


                                                                                                                                Placement of leading and trailing values or icons

                                                                                                                                Users expect the placement of minimum and maximum value of the slider to be consistent across all apps.

                                                                                                                                For languages that are displayed from left-to-right, the smallest value for the range is placed on the left and the largest value is placed on the right.

                                                                                                                                For languages that are displayed from right to left, the smallest value for the range is placed on the right and the largest value is placed on the left.

                                                                                                                                  

                                                                                                                                Behavior

                                                                                                                                Users can select a value with sliders by: dragging the knob, selecting directly from the track, or selecting the knob and navigating along the track with keyboard navigation.

                                                                                                                                As the value on the slider increases, the section of the track between the minimum value to the knob is filled.


                                                                                                                                Dragging the knob
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                User selects a value by dragging the knob along the track.

                                                                                                                                Select directly from the track
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                User selects a value by tapping on the track.

                                                                                                                                Select and move with keyboard
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Use tab and shift+tab to navigate between knobs

                                                                                                                                Use page up and page down or fn + arrow up or fn + arrow down to navigate forward or backwards by ten steps

                                                                                                                                Wrapping and truncation

                                                                                                                                Labels for sliders should be three words or less, but can be longer in specific contexts. In this scenario, long labels will wrap to the next line and should be top aligned with the value (if applicable).

                                                                                                                                States

                                                                                                                                Simple

                                                                                                                                Enabled
                                                                                                                                Active
                                                                                                                                Active + value label
                                                                                                                                Disabled

                                                                                                                                Segment

                                                                                                                                Enabled
                                                                                                                                Active
                                                                                                                                Active + value label
                                                                                                                                Disabled

                                                                                                                                Range

                                                                                                                                Enabled
                                                                                                                                Active
                                                                                                                                Active + value label
                                                                                                                                Disabled

                                                                                                                                Icons

                                                                                                                                Enabled
                                                                                                                                Active
                                                                                                                                Active + value label
                                                                                                                                Disabled
